伦敦维多利亚公园将举办更多活动和更大的节日https://www.nme.com/news/music/londons-victoria-park-set-for-more-events-and-bigger-festivals-3577965?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=londons-victoria-park-set-更多活动和更大的节日Emma WilkesFri, 26 Jan 2024 20:54:53 +0000 FestivalsMusic NewsNewsAll Points East https://www.nme.com/?p=3577965 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>东伦敦公园现在每年可以举办 12 场活动</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/londons-victoria-park-set-for-more-events-and-bigger-festivals-3577965">伦敦维多利亚公园将举办更多活动和更大的节日，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/All-Points-East-header-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>伦敦维多利亚公园未来将举办更多活动，这些活动的最大容量也将增加。</p><p>该公园目前举办<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/all-points-east">All Points East</a>和 Field Day 等活动，这两项活动的规模可能会更大，现在大型活动的容量已从 5,000 人增加到 20,000 人。目前可容纳 500 人的中型活动也将增加至 5,000 人。</p><p>除此之外，东伦敦公园可举办的活动数量现已从每年 10 场增加到 12 场。</p><p>尽管如此，一些当地人仍表示反对该计划。据<em><a href="https://romanroadlondon.com/tower-hamlets-council-increase-major-events-victoria-park/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《罗马路》</a></em>报道，社区团体“维多利亚公园之友”表示，他们“认为增加活动规模和频率对公园使用者和居民都不利。</p><p>该组织表示：“大型活动非常吵闹，给公园使用者和居民，特别是幼儿和老年人带来极大的困扰。”</p><p>然而，陶尔哈姆莱茨市长卢特弗·拉赫曼（Lutfur Ra​​hman）辩称，市议会“别无选择”，只能增加维多利亚公园的节日容量，作为创收的一种方式，但这仍然符合当地人的利益。</p><p>他说：“我们必须尽可能多地从我们的资产、我们的合同、我们的公园以及我们在这个行政区所做的一切中榨取资源，因为我们必须保护我们的居民。” [通过<a href="https://www.timeout.com/london/news/all-points-east-has-revealed-its-first-headliners-for-2024-120123" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>超时</em></a>] </p><figure id="attachment_3495144" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3495144" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3495144" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/All-Points-East-Stage.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/All-Points-East-Stage.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/All-Points-East-Stage-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/All-Points-East-Stage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/All-Points-East-Stage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/All-Points-East-Stage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/All-Points-East-Stage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3495144" class="wp-caption-text">英国伦敦 - 8 月 25 日：2023 年 8 月 25 日在英国伦敦维多利亚公园举行的 2023 年 All Points East Festival 西舞台景观。 （摄影：Burak Cingi/Redferns）</figcaption></figure><p>到目前为止，今年夏天的 All Points East 已经宣布了两套表演。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">洛伊尔·卡纳 (Loyle Carner)</a>是 11 月第一位确认的头条新闻人物，将于 8 月 17 日与他一起亮相的艺术家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/loyle-carner">洛伊尔·卡纳 (Loyle Carner)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nas">Nas、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ezra-collective">Ezra Collective、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sainte">Sainé</a> 、Joe James、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enny">ENNY</a>和 Navy Blue。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lcd-soundsystem">LCD Soundsystem</a>已确认将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-all-points-east-london-uk-tour-line-up-pixies-tickets-3551502">成为 8 月 23 日的头条新闻。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jai-paul">Jai Paul</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pixies">Pixies</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/floating-points">Floating Points</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jockstrap">Jockstrap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/NATION-OF-LANGUAGE">Nation of Language</a>等乐队将加入其中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/SOFIA-KOURTESIS">Sofia Kourtesis</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eyedress">Eyedress</a>的现场表演 - 门票当天可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fuber-one-presents-all-points-east-lcd-soundsystem-london-23-08-2024%2Fevent%2F37005F7DFE4F7083" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。</p><p>去年的音乐节上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stage-times-for-the-strokes-and-yeah-yeah-yeahs-at-all-points-east-2023-3487448">，The Strokes、Yeah Yeah Yeahs、The Walkmen 等乐队登上了舞台</a>。</p><p>尽管存在声音问题， <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-strokes-all-points-east-2023-london-victoria-park-review-setlist-photos-3488878">The Strokes 的演出在<em>NME</em>四星评论中被描述为“出色的平衡表演”</a> 。它补充道：“纽约独立偶像们为 All Point East 带来了大热门和不太明显的选择，因为他们再次以音量水平进行战斗。”</p><p>作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/stormzy-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3485854">“This Is What We Mean”日</a>的一部分， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stormzy">Stormzy</a>还表演了一场职业生涯亮点表演。在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stormzy">Stormzy</a>在 2023 年 All Points East 表演的四星评价中， <em>NME</em>写道，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/stormzy-live-in-london-setlist-photos-3485854">说唱歌手的“雨中回归”带来了“节奏的改变”</a> 。它补充道：“两幕表演可能会疏远更多休闲粉丝，但最终为 Stormzy 年度唯一的英国演出带来回报。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/londons-victoria-park-set-for-more-events-and-bigger-festivals-3577965">伦敦维多利亚公园将举办更多活动和更大的节日，</a>这一消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
